10
00:01:03,625 --> 00:01:04,275
Aah...!

11
00:01:18,225 --> 00:01:18,850
Nefer !

12
00:01:18,925 --> 00:01:19,275
Hé !

13
00:01:19,275 --> 00:01:19,975
Tenez bon !

14
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,475
En savoir trop...

15
00:01:32,975 --> 00:01:35,425
